#Repeated Measures ANOVA on Live Carbon by Treatment across Years
live_lme <- lme(carbon ~ Treatment * year, random= ~ year|Plot, data=live, method="ML", control=list(opt="optim"))
#summary(live_lme)
anova(live_lme)
